# Day 48 – Compare & Decide Builder

## Overview
Built a premium single-page **Compare & Decide Builder** that helps users compare multiple options using customizable decision criteria and dynamic ranking.

## Features
- Compare multiple options
- Adjustable criteria weights
- Live ranking updates
- Interactive comparison dashboard
- Decision score visualization
- Sources & References panel
- "How this was researched" section
- Responsive dark mode UI

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

## Learning Outcomes
- Learned how weighted decision matrices work
- Built a real-time comparison engine using JavaScript
- Improved responsive dashboard design
- Organized research sources into a structured interface
- Enhanced interactive UI with dynamic updates

